title: Awkward Drama at Office Christmas Party + Draft Favorite Christmas Movies + Raymundo Won A Big Trip from the Company + Bobby’s Top 5 TV Shows of 2021

description:
Bobby heard from a little birdy that members of the show were embarrassed at the Office Christmas Party. We investigate what went down. We draft the best Christmas movies of all-time. We found out that Raymundo won a big trip from the company and Bobby shares his Top 5 TV shows of the year.
